column36: Patient came for her 6 month fu with Dr. Perez. The DXMM results took this morning was good, her skin healed very well. Patient asked if her fibroadenoma on her right breast was taken out from the surgery. Dr. Perez verified that the fibroadenoma was benign and was not removed from the surgery. Because it is benign it does not need to be removed. 6month fu with a dxmm on the right breast and fu with dr. Perez.
